title: Finish Line FiberLink Tubeless Sealant gets a refresh with new Pro Latex Formula
content:
Finish Line FiberLink tubeless sealant came out of the gate with some bold claims. Initially claiming that it would last the life of the tire, they eventually walked back those claims but continued to sell the latex-free formula.
